metadata.description: Here are the top 10 values of a freelancer. On the top of the list is Consistency. Consistency is not just about the work we deliver to our clients. Consistency is also the way we treat and service our clients, our workflows and our communications. When we underpromise and overdeliver, , we can expect a consistent pipeline of projects from them. Why would they turn to someone else when you have delivered an exceptional service?
metadata.name: Consistency
